{"tid":450345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大王宋本中: 劇集內容要收歛, 不能教壞小朋友","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T06:51:14.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91f44654a7aa3387363a6f2df3aabf1a4e2eba9b","tid":450345,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/129025/-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91-%E5%AE%8B%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%AD%E6%84%9F%E6%BF%80%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E9%BD%8A%E5%AD%AD%E9%91%8A-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D%E5%89%8D%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F129025%2F-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591-%25E5%25AE%258B%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%2585%2584%25E5%25BC%259F%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%25AD%25AD%25E9%2591%258A-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2584%25B6%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-&d=ttNQWDG3zbjj93Fe4ww0CePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=eb99d28d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/129025/-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91-%E5%AE%8B%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%AD%E6%84%9F%E6%BF%80%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E9%BD%8A%E5%AD%AD%E9%91%8A-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D%E5%89%8D%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-</a></span><br />\n<br />\n對於有傳《反黑》因有大陸資金，故拍攝時受到不少政治壓力，宋本中澄清所有投資者都是香港公司。「自己又唔係知識份子，書又唔係讀得多，所以完全唔存在用劇去講啲咩歷史。」他又指出全劇唔煙唔粗口，並不是為了要通過內地的審批，而是作為一個媒體工作者應有的責任。「小朋友三歲都可以上網，同埋我自己細個都係睇太多廣告所以學食煙，到而家都戒唔到，我係咪仲要去害下一代呢？食煙喺《反黑》係咪咁重要呢？唔係囉。陳小春都曾經講過無諗《古惑仔》咁大影響，某程度上亦教壞咗一班人，以為做古惑仔好威，搵到錢，其實唔係。」觀眾有留意的話，每個角色離去之後都有一段自白，除了更詳細交代背景之外，眾人都會苦口婆心叫大家唔好學壞，教育意義何其重。宋本中一直以電視劇的標準去拍攝《反黑》，目的是希望有日可以喺電視播出。「所有嘢都係我決定，無嘢可能左右我，我真非常咁『盟塞』。」"},{"pid":"976fafd38b781495348fb75aa2bea3bc2818041c","tid":450345,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebb1817fa434cce032aa510d38528a3066e288a8","tid":450345,"uid":3773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/crHs9WixtSI/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FcrHs9WixtSI%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d1b8695e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3363a0232205d7855283af5296afcabcb911d77","tid":450345,"uid":16818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"一集都無睇過<br />\n大陸劇"},{"pid":"de10d25f6d8a3541a936ba10c103b04fc9128d29","tid":450345,"uid":9681,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"咁做乜撚黑社會題材呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15c29f922dcd168d4e43487a3a78add61e031fe","tid":450345,"uid":29742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁做乜撚黑社會題材呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTvb黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係講：正衰人，你會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡d都係講仆街"},{"pid":"5493b7cc9d4424e7685c3bb464f9fc64f95d9808","tid":450345,"uid":44454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁做乜撚黑社會題材呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為要抹黑英國，下次可能係廉政公署係共產黨要求成立"},{"pid":"021953ed2934ca455ff0f586de0a6968a8a9ef3b","tid":450345,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"精...精...茶餐廳"}]}